sentences.english: Like every paradigm throughout history, at some point or another, things change.

sentences.english: It is the longest standing example of interagency cooperation in the UN system.

sentences.english: African delegates said they hope to learn from Vietnam's agricultural example.

sentences.english: Mr Hu hopes Xinhe will be an example to the world.

sentences.english: Up to now, China has been the poster child for market-oriented economic reform success.
